# Assets Directory

This directory contains assets used in the VeriCore documentation, such as images, diagrams, and other media files.

## Directory Structure

- `images/` - Images, diagrams, screenshots, and other visual assets
  - Use descriptive filenames (e.g., `architecture-diagram.png`, `workflow-sequence.svg`)
  - Prefer SVG for diagrams when possible for scalability
  - Optimize images for web when possible

## Usage in Documentation

Reference assets in markdown files using relative paths:

```markdown
![Alt text](assets/images/example.png)
```

For images in the docs root, use:
```markdown
![Alt text](../assets/images/example.png)
```

